com.bmd.android.collection.entry

Interface SparseLongArrayEntry

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IntSparseEntry, IntSparseLongEntry, SparseEntry, SparseLongEntry

    public interface SparseLongArrayEntry
extends IntSparseLongEntry
    This interface defines a SparseEntry associated with a SparseLongArray collection.

    Created by davide on 3/10/14.
